{"tid":1927741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：未來兩星期會有大量香港留學生返港，新一輪輸入個案數字會急升","createTime":"2020-03-16T03:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:23:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"349d54c90d70aedeaf8f45c16448e3d2c721a202","tid":1927741,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在一個電台節目表示，未來兩星期應該會有大量香港留學生返港，估計新一輪輸入個案數字會急升。他建議所有曾離境香港的人士，回港後都要接受家居檢疫，否則會追不上疫情發展。他又建議，拒絕來自疫情較嚴重國家的旅客入境。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良表示，輸入個案增多，社區難免會危機四伏，所以對本地傳播鏈短時間內能切斷，感到悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n至於英國應對疫情的政策，何栢良認為，若香港以同樣政策處理，將會車毀人亡。他說人命最寶貴，政府一定要用強力措施，加強社交隔離，包括停工、停課等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514693-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514693-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=40cc67e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514693-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a51b10e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514693-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f5ee47b778b8e419fcb122a913d2a8d767e7cf1c","tid":1927741,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341ad7e4bd0c37762330dd0632520059cb53b30","tid":1927741,"uid":76341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"停工停課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf8b5cb8cd50603177cae381ba5b57af57e9083","tid":1927741,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac